                        <interp inst="t18410823-name-896" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PEORUM</persName>
                  </hi>. This is my handkerchief—it has my name on it—I was tipsy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Where had you been? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> At a public-house.</p>
